lead_paragraph: BANKS--Seymour. Born 3 Oct. 1917, died 29 May 1996 Hard to believe it's been 20 years! We miss you every day. And no, it's "not better than a poke in the eye with a sharp stick". With love, Miriam, Hannah, Joel, David and the ganze mispocha. 1/3
